thread.title: Match Group’s Profit Shows Steep Rise

author: Georgia Wells
title: Match Group’s Profit Shows Steep Rise

organizations.name: match group’s profit shows steep rise match group inc.

text:
Match Group Inc. on Tuesday reported its strongest quarterly results as a publicly traded company, with net profit at the internet data company rising nearly fivefold from a year ago as users signed up to pay for its Tinder app.
The results come as Match faces a new challenge, with social-media giant Facebook Inc. announcing last month that it is starting a dating service on its platform.
